quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,"Maa ki ngantinora kodduruyee, ki wi'ia: Si Allah feewnuno mi, mi jeyeteno e hulu…ìe Mo …ìen. Mi …óoftoo yamirooje Makko, mi wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko."
  39,58,"Maa ki yelora wi'ugol, nde ki yi'ata lepte …óen: Si feere ruttagol aduna no woodannoo lam, mi tuubanayno Allah, mi jeyee e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe golle …ìen."
  39,59,"∆äum gasatira no faalira…óaa non feewirde ! Tawde Aayeeje Amen …óen aruno e maa…óa, fennu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen, yeddi Aayeeje Makko …óen e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  39,60,"√ëalnde Darngal, a yi'oyay fenunoo…ìe e hoore Allah …ìen, …ìe dammbi sirku e …ìi…ó…óo e Makko, hi…ìe …ìawli geece, hakkee ko …ìe malkisaa. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde mawnintinanii…ìe gom…óingol Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on? Ko ton tigiri, woni weerde ma…ì…ìe."
  39,61,"Allah hisinira hulu…ìe Mo …óoftii ha…óitii …ìen, e lepte, O naadaugol …ìe ka maloore Aljanna. Bone lepte memataa …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni ko sunoytoo, fii ko fe∆¥∆¥i e ge…ìoy aduna."
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tagu…óo kala huunde, wanaa go…ó…óo go…ó…óum goo. Ko Kanko kadi woni Fawtii…óo kala huunde, O Toppitoo fii mayre, O wa…óira nde, no O haajiri."
  39,63,"Ko Kanko tun, jogitii ngaluuji mo∆¥∆¥ere …óin, ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Himo ye…óa …ói Mo O haajani, O …óawa …ói Mo O muuyi. Yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Allah …ìen non, ko …ìen woni hayru…ìe …ìen. Tawde …ìe fa…óii gom…óingol e nguurndam ma…ì…ìe …óam aduna, e hoore …ìe naatoyay …ìe heddoo ka Yiite, laakara."
  39,64,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe jokku…ìe maa, fii rewugol sanamuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin: E on yamiray lam, onon …ìee majju…ìe fii Joomi mun, nde mi rewata ko woori Allah? Anndee ko Allah tun, hanndi e reweede, mi rewataa, si wanaa Kanko."
  39,65,"Gom…óii Allah wahayinii maa…óa, an Nulaa…óo, O wahayini kadi e Nulaa…ìe adinoo…ìe ma …ìen: si a kafidii e Allah go…ó…óum goo, ko pellet, golle maa mo∆¥∆¥e …óen bonay; jeye…óaa e hayru…ìe aduna …ìen, sabu hayru…ìe diina maa, hayroyaa kadi e lepte laakara …óen."
  39,66,"Ko Allah tun, si a reway, hara a kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óum goo, jeye…óaa e yettoo…ìe Mo neemajji …ói O neemini e maa…óa …óin."
  39,67,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen mawniniraali Allah, no O haaniri mawninireede, tuma …ìe kafidunoo Mo e taguuji Makko lo'u…ói, …ìe yejjiti wonnde no jeyaa e kattane Makko ngal, tawde leydi ndin e ko woni mayri kon : immorde e pelle e le…ó…óe e can…ói e boyli, fow e mun, √ëalnde Darngal, ko e tamannde Makko wonata, kammuuli …óin jee…ói…ói kadi, fow majji taggiree √±aamo Makko ngon. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O laa…ìii O toowii kon ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen fi…ìata wowla e Makko."